Project -> VB Stream (E- Classroom)

## Project Overview

VB Steam E-Classroom is an education management platform designed for schools 
and higher education institutions. The platform enables administrators to manage schools, 
classes, teachers, subjects, and class schedules while providing students with access to online learning. 
The system also supports multiple user panels, allowing administrators, schools, teachers, and students to access 
features based on their roles and permissions.

## Key Features

- Multi-School Management
- Multiple User Panels (Admin, School, Teacher, and Student)
- School Management
- Class Management
- Teacher Management
- Student Management
- Subject Management
- Teacher & Subject Assignment
- Class Scheduling & Timetable
- Online Classes
- Role-Based Access Control
- User Authentication
- Notifications
- Admin Dashboard

